    <briefdescription>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Saturates the PFIFO queue with irrelevant commands and performs a handful of draws designed to render efficiently without being fill rate limited. Intended to identify unintentional stalls in processing the PFIFO command buffer. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
